                        <interp inst="t18471025-name-187" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM TYLER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City policeman</hi> 373.) I took the prisoner, he told me where he lived—I went there and found this article in his box.</p>
